LabSeq Calculator!

This page allows you to explore the LabSeq sequence, a mathematical sequence defined by specific rules.

The LabSeq sequence is defined as follows:

  • n=0 => l(0) = 0
  • n=1 => l(1) = 1
  • n=2 => l(2) = 0
  • n=3 => l(3) = 1
  • n>3 => l(n) = l(n-4) + l(n-3)
